cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper deals with analyzing video advertisements using human-annotated features and common video processing techniques. This involves machine learning classification tasks, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of Multimedia (cs.MM), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
